snippet.title: The Report: The Eastwind Creature
snippet.description:
This game is based on a horror story experienced in person, in this game you will find terror and entertainment.

THE REPORT: The Eastwind Creature

A road traveler heads into Eastwind in search of a creature from a local legend to do a report.

INFORMATION

First person game

Terror and jumpscares

If you are a person sensitive to scares, this game could be bad for you.

Game made by one person

10 minutes of duration aprox

It's not a very long game


RELEASE IN SEPTEMBER 25th
